Package rpgonline.net.logon

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UserServer
    A interface for managing login details.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpLogonServer
    A server using POST over HTTP to perform login operations.
    HttpsLogonServer
    A server using POST over HTTPS to perform login operations.
    LocalLogonServer
    A client side logon server that should be used Only for testing
    LocalLogonServer.User
    A class representing a user.
    MultiLogonServer
    A server that supports multiple connections and will pick the best connection.
    MultiLogonServer.DownServer
    A server used if not other server can be found.
